name: TeamEXtension
overview:
TeamEXtension provides companies managed, cost-effective Java development and maintenance teams. A team is composed of dedicated Java/J2EE developers and one shared IT project manager.

Our business model provides clients with the needed resources they need to run their daily IT tasks. TeamEXtension handles both software development and system maintenance. Included with every team is an experienced project manager, so the client does not need to stress out about daily project and people management. The project manager also acts as an IT adviser, to help the client make informed decisions about current and future technology initiatives. The team members are dedicated to the client, so the client’s projects are the priority and focus. The team is easy to setup and requires no long term contract. Get a complete, cost effective software development team specially designed for small and medium sized businesses.
